title: Win8 x86
description:
Windows 8 x86 version 6,2 build 8102.109 with Windows 8 BluePoison so you can change the control panel to classic .................

Tested 2 games on this GTA iv and Maffia 2 got higher FPS on this vs Windows 7 .......	

Remember to use programs in Compatibility Mode.. RightClick on the icon on a program you want use click properties Compatibility and set it to Windows 7 ..... I got my antivirus and other programs to run without errors :)
